---
title: Thai Style Chicken Curry with courgette and fragrant rice
description: This Thai-inspired chicken curry is creamy, fragrant, and as spicy as you like. Lime rice adds a satiating element while the courgette and onion add vibrancy, health and crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W31_IE_IEXQC0100-2_Main__3high-fb208b4f.jpg
